                     <persName id="t18451124-name-298" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18451124-name-298" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451124-name-298" type="surname" value="EVANS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18451124-name-298" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY EVANS</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> George Parker slept in Smith's bed—he was before the Magistrate, and discharged—a boy named Near slept with James—he has since absconded from the workhouse.</p>
